      "body": "我大概知道了，`$getConfig().env.deviceWidth`这个值貌似和屏幕尺寸不一致，跟`flex`没有关系\n\n``` html\n<template>\n  <div>\n    <text class='hello'>hello</text>\n    <text class='hello' style='width: {{$getConfig().env.deviceWidth}}px;'>hello</text>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<style>\n  .hello {\n    border-style: solid;\n    border-width: 1px;\n    border-color: #333;\n  }\n</style>\n```\n\n 三者的效果\n![229789728462629724](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/7157346/17501733/61ae674c-5e14-11e6-9d0b-4ee00956f1ba.jpg)\n![2016080901](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/7157346/17503367/e5d2bf7a-5e21-11e6-999d-59c2d0252164.png)\n![qq 20160809093420](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/7157346/17501743/7e29c056-5e14-11e6-944d-cfd35d24478b.png)\n"
