  "body": "`display:flex;` 和`postion:fixed`，在游览器和app中的显示效果不同\n\n``` html\n<template>\n  <div>\n\n    <div class='flex'>\n      <div class='flex-item'>\n        <text>1</text>\n      </div>\n      <div class='flex-item'>\n        <text>1</text>\n      </div>\n      <div class='flex-item'>\n        <text>1</text>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class='flex' style='position: fixed; bottom: 0; width: {{$getConfig().env.deviceWidth}}px;'>\n      <div class='flex-item'>\n        <text>2</text>\n      </div>\n      <div class='flex-item'>\n        <text>2</text>\n      </div>\n      <div class='flex-item'>\n        <text>2</text>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n\n<style>\n  .flex {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: row;\n    border-style: solid;\n    border-width: 1px;\n    border-color: #f00;\n  }\n  .flex-item {\n    flex: 1;\n    border-style: solid;\n    border-width: 1px;\n    border-color: #333;\n  }\n\n</style>\n\n```\n\n游览器效果：\n![qq 20160808160240](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/7157346/17473204/cc225446-5d81-11e6-9cd9-b5d8ac256160.png)\n\napp效果（android和ios都一样）\n![img_1003](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/7157346/17473206/cd9cbf00-5d81-11e6-9433-fd2a0a8ff032.PNG)\n"
